        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nAt this stage for Casablanca, only integration created blocking bugs should be fixed/merged. Looking at https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Casablanca+Release+Integration+Testing+Status, RealTime PM cases are marked pass and completed. \n\nGiven this, should this fix be required only in master?",
