        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nDo we plan to deliver some fixes to the Casablanca maintenance release? If so, maybe we can add this fix, too. In that case where should we push the change? To my understanding we can push it to casablanca branch and then (if maintenance release is going to be released) change versions in OOM deployment and other places.",
